dismissalText.commentary: Marlon Samuels c Taibu b Dabengwa 43 (43b 1x4 3x6 43m) SR: 100

dismissalText.commentary: Denesh Ramdin c Chigumbura b Chibhabha 16 (18b 1x4 0x6 23m) SR: 88.88

dismissalText.commentary: Rawl Lewis c Masakadza b Chibhabha 19 (18b 0x4 1x6 23m) SR: 105.55
